            "subtitle": "",
            "description": "<p><strong>Honey with Super Power</strong>: High Potent Spring Harvest, renowned for its hallucinating and psychedelic effects, only available in limited stock. </p><p><strong>Crafted with love: </strong>Once dearly guarded by the Himalayan people, our hallucinogenic honey is carefully harvested, bottled, and packed in Nepal, with perfection shining through every step, from nectar collection to packaging.</p><p><strong>Traceability and Certification:</strong> Each jar of our premium mad honey is traceable to its source. Scan the QR code on the label to access official test reports and mad honey <a href=\"/pages/grayanotoxin\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"grayanotoxin\">grayanotoxin</a> analysis to find out the exact origin of honey. </p>",
            "button_text": "Shop Mad Honey",
