          "settings": {
            "title": "Express Worldwide Shipping!",
            "subtitle": "",
            "description": "<p>We are committed to delivering the finest mad honey from Nepal to you as quickly as possible.</p><p>Every jar is packed in our GMP-certified facility and shipped to our warehouses in the USA. Orders are dispatched within 2 business days, through DHL Express and USPS. We offer free express shipping worldwide, orders are fully tracked and you will receive an email with your tracking information once your order has been dispatched.</p>",
